trans-unit.source: Passed to custom WSDL exporters and importers to enable customization of the metadata export and import processes for a WSDL endpoint.
trans-unit.target: Doorgegeven aan de aangepaste WSDL exporteurs en importers inschakelen aanpassing van de metagegevens van exporteren en importeren processen voor een WSDL-eindpunt.

trans-unit.source: The WsdlEndpointConversionContext class represents the context in which the custom WSDL for an endpoint is either exported using <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IWsdlExportExtension?displayProperty=fullName> or imported using <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IWsdlImportExtension?displayProperty=fullName>.
trans-unit.target: De klasse WsdlEndpointConversionContext geeft de context waarin de aangepaste WSDL voor een eindpunt is dat ofwel geëxporteerd of <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IWsdlExportExtension?displayProperty=fullName>met behulp van <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IWsdlImportExtension?displayProperty=fullName>.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IWsdlImportExtension?displayProperty=fullName> geïmporteerd</xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IWsdlExportExtension?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: The following properties enable you to retrieve the WSDL document object model for the current WSDL: - The <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlEndpointConversionContext.ContractConversionContext%2A> property gets the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlContractConversionContext?displayProperty=fullName> for the endpoint contract.
trans-unit.target: De volgende eigenschappen kunnen u voor het ophalen van het WSDL-document objectmodel voor de huidige WSDL: - de <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlEndpointConversionContext.ContractConversionContext%2A>eigenschap haalt de <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlContractConversionContext?displayProperty=fullName>voor het contract van het eindpunt.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlContractConversionContext?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlEndpointConversionContext.ContractConversionContext%2A>

trans-unit.source: - The <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlEndpointConversionContext.Endpoint%2A> property gets the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ServiceEndpoint?displayProperty=fullName> for the current endpoint.
trans-unit.target: -De <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlEndpointConversionContext.Endpoint%2A>eigenschap haalt de <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ServiceEndpoint?displayProperty=fullName>voor het huidige endpoint.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ServiceEndpoint?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlEndpointConversionContext.Endpoint%2A>

trans-unit.source: - The <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlEndpointConversionContext.WsdlBinding%2A> property gets the binding for the current endpoint.
trans-unit.target: -De <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlEndpointConversionContext.WsdlBinding%2A>eigenschap haalt de binding voor het huidige endpoint.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlEndpointConversionContext.WsdlBinding%2A>

trans-unit.source: - The <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlEndpointConversionContext.WsdlPort%2A> property gets the port for the current endpoint.
trans-unit.target: -De <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlEndpointConversionContext.WsdlPort%2A>eigenschap haalt de poort voor het huidige endpoint.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlEndpointConversionContext.WsdlPort%2A>

trans-unit.source: - - The following methods enable you to add or remove custom WSDL elements to the appropriate scopes in the exported or imported WSDL: - The <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlEndpointConversionContext.GetFaultBinding%2A> method returns the fault binding for the specified fault.
trans-unit.target: --De volgende methoden kunnen u toevoegen of verwijderen van aangepaste WSDL-elementen op de juiste bereiken in de geëxporteerde of geïmporteerde WSDL: - de <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlEndpointConversionContext.GetFaultBinding%2A>methode retourneert de foutbinding voor het opgegeven foutdomein.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlEndpointConversionContext.GetFaultBinding%2A>

trans-unit.source: - The <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlEndpointConversionContext.GetFaultDescription%2A> method returns the fault for the specified fault binding.
trans-unit.target: -De <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlEndpointConversionContext.GetFaultDescription%2A>methode retourneert de fout voor de binding opgegeven foutdomein.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlEndpointConversionContext.GetFaultDescription%2A>

trans-unit.source: - The <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlEndpointConversionContext.GetMessageBinding%2A> method returns the message binding for the specified message.
trans-unit.target: -De <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlEndpointConversionContext.GetMessageBinding%2A>methode retourneert de bericht-binding voor het opgegeven bericht.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlEndpointConversionContext.GetMessageBinding%2A>

trans-unit.source: - The <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlEndpointConversionContext.GetMessageDescription%2A> method returns the message for the specified message binding.
trans-unit.target: -De <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlEndpointConversionContext.GetMessageDescription%2A>methode retourneert het bericht voor de binding opgegeven bericht.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlEndpointConversionContext.GetMessageDescription%2A>

trans-unit.source: - The <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlEndpointConversionContext.GetOperationBinding%2A> method returns the operation binding for the specified operation.
trans-unit.target: -De <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlEndpointConversionContext.GetOperationBinding%2A>methode retourneert de bewerkingsbinding voor de opgegeven bewerking.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlEndpointConversionContext.GetOperationBinding%2A>

trans-unit.source: - The <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlEndpointConversionContext.GetOperationDescription%2A> method returns the operation for the specified operation binding.
